                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">Office of <persName>Davis, Peixotto &amp; Co.</persName></p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>Nos. 3 &amp; 5 Street</placeName>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>Corner of Superior Street</placeName>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>Cleveland</placeName>, <date>April 8th\n                1864</date>.</p>\n            <p><persName>Geo. A. Davis</persName>.</p>\n            <p>\n                <placeName>NEW YORK</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p><persName role=\"author\">B. F. Peixotto</persName>.</p>\n            <p><placeName>CLEVELAND</placeName>.</p>\n            <p>Rev and Dear Friend</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Your favor by Express<lb/> enclosing the 14 numbers of the<lb/>\n                Jewish Miscellany is at hand<lb/> I find the first number so much<lb/> damaged by\n                wet and the changes in the package<lb/> excessive that I have induced<lb/> the\n                Express Co to make amends<lb/> pay for another copy of <persName><hi\n                        rend=\"underline\">Caleb</hi><lb/>\n                    <hi rend=\"underline\">Asher</hi></persName> and bring it to me<lb/> free of\n                charge. Will you therefore<lb/> please send me by American<lb/> Express said copy to\n                replace<lb/> the one damaged—pay for which<lb/> and for the others please find<lb/>\n                herewith. Enclosed find<lb/> $14.25, $10 to pay for my<lb/> subscription to the\n                    <persName>Aguilar</persName> work<lb/> $4.25 for the Miscellany</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p35m62t13/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
